b'{"data_headers":{"result_code":1},"data":{"information":{"article_id":2756,"category_name":"News","pr_category_id":"1","title_name":"Regarding an Issue with Summoning","message":"<div>We have confirmed that from around <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1641017100\\"><\/span> to <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1641017940\\"><\/span>, there were some cases in which an additional summon occurred when the player selected Try Again after the &quot;Failed to connect to the server.&quot; error displayed when performing a summon on the summon screen.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>In some cases the animation for the additional summon did not play, but we have confirmed that the summoned adventurers and\/or dragons were received normally.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Note: You can confirm your summon history by tapping Summon History in the Help\/Support screen in the menu. The last 30 summons made within the past two weeks (14 days) are displayed.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>This issue has been resolved.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>We will send all players who selected Try Again and performed an additional summon during the period in which this issue occurred the wyrmite, summon vouchers, or diamantium that was consumed when the additional summon was performed.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Affected players can claim these items from their goodie box.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0Affected Players<\/div><div>All players who selected Try Again and performed an additional summon from around <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1641017100\\"><\/span> to around <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1641017940\\"><\/span>.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.<\/div>","start_time":1641880800,"prev_article_id":"2750","next_article_id":"2759","image_path":"","update_time":1641865031}}}'